rigerator","hintsAndTricks":["If a blowtorch is not available, meringues can be browned under the grill. To do this, serve in ceramic dishes, and grill under a medium heat for <nobr>30-60 seconds.<\/nobr> Glasses may crack under high heat of a grill.","Substitute lemons with oranges.","Substitute cinnamon biscuits with butter biscuits or gluten-free biscuits.","Substitute lemon with juice of <nobr>2 lemons<\/nobr> and skip <nobr>step 2.<\/nobr>"],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","6 portions"]}